org.sakaiproject.site.cover

Class SiteService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.site.cover.SiteService
  • Deprecated. 
    Static covers should not be used in favour of injection or lookup via the component manager. This cover will be removed in a later version of the Kernel

    public class SiteService
extends Object

    SiteService is a static Cover for the SiteService; see that interface for usage details.
